{"word":"G5543 - χρηστός - chrēstós - khrase-tos' - Better","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">χρηστός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">chrēstós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">khrase-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Better</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"மெதுவான, நல்ல, நன்மையான, தயவான, தயையுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"1. fit for use, useful; virtuous, good"},{"paragraph":"2. manageable, mild, pleasant"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5530 - χράομαι - chráomai - khrah'-om-ahee/5530\">G5530</a>; <i>employed</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>useful</i> (in manner or morals): - better, easy, good (-ness), gracious, kind.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G5541/5541\">G5541</a>, <a href=\"#/G5542/5542\">G5542</a>, <a href=\"#/G5543/5543\">G5543</a>, <a href=\"#/G5544/5544\">G5544</a>"}]}